    {
      "id": "s001",
      "text": "Lesson 69.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "第69课。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s002",
      "text": "The Car Race.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "汽车比赛。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s003",
      "text": "Listen to the tape, then answer this question.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "听录音，然后回答这个问题。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s004",
      "text": "Which car was the winner in 1995?",
      "translation": {
        "text": "1995年哪辆车获胜了？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s005",
      "text": "There is a car race near our town every year.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "我们镇附近每年都有一场汽车比赛。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s006",
      "text": "In 1995 there was a very big race.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "1995年举行了一场规模很大的比赛。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s007",
      "text": "There were hundreds of people there.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "那里有数百人。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s008",
      "text": "My wife and I were at the race.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "我和妻子都在比赛现场。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s009",
      "text": "Our friends Julie and Jack were there too.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "我们的朋友朱莉和杰克也在那里。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s010",
      "text": "You can see us in the crowd.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "你可以在人群中看到我们。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s011",
      "text": "We are standing on the left.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "我们站在左边。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s012",
      "text": "There were 20 cars in the race.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "参加比赛的有20辆车。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s013",
      "text": "There were English cars, French cars, German cars, Italian cars, American cars, and Japanese cars.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "有英国车、法国车、德国车、意大利车、美国车和日本车。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s014",
      "text": "It was an exciting finish.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "比赛的结尾激动人心。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s015",
      "text": "The winner was Billy Stewart.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "获胜者是比利·斯图尔特。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s016",
      "text": "He was in car number 15.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "他开的是15号车。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s017",
      "text": "Five other cars were just behind him.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "另外五辆车紧跟在他后面。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s018",
      "text": "On the way home, my wife said to me, Don't drive so quickly.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "回家的路上，妻子对我说：“别开得这么快。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s019",
      "text": "You're not Billy Stewart.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "你又不是比利·斯图尔特。”"
      }
    }
  ],
